data.description: Park West Home! 1,667 sq. ft. with 3 bedrooms 2 baths and 2 car garage. The home also has a paid for solar system to help reduce your electric bill! Formal living room and dining room. Kitchen is open to the family room that has a glass slider to the covered patio. Master bedroom has walk in closet with French door to access backyard and Aquaterra hot tub. Custom garage cabinets and flooring. Mature peach and lemon trees. 2023-10-07
